milestone.title: Speech to Text
milestone.description: Program can convert lecture audio to english text.

issue.body:
Included Google Cloud API calls needed to run Speech to Text. Also
included command line arguments and Google Cloud Storage uploading for
large files.

Also included a few WAV files for testing. The program outputs to transcription.txt by default, and the example output for readingcomp.wav is included.
